<!-- Restore state: "True" uses the stored find requests. "False" does not restore stored requests. -->
<!-- Option state: "True" performs find without indexes (may improve performance when found set is already small). "False" uses indexes. -->
<!-- RequestRow operation: "Include" | "Exclude" (omit matching records) -->
<!-- Multiple Criteria elements can be added within a RequestRow. Multiple RequestRow elements act as OR conditions. -->
<!-- Equivalent to a logical AND search against the existing found set. -->
